    "description": "Glimmer Chain是一款基于技能的平台游戏，你将成为一个带有钩和链的充能机器人。<br><br>在一座荒凉的城市中，一台具有人工智能的烤面包机决定制造机器人，唯一的目的是照亮并赋予城市生机。玩家必须控制这些机器人，摆动并推进自己穿越建筑物，将他们的能量传输到发电机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/8b070a742560a61567182821f37a178a.poster.avif?t=1712662018\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/8b070a742560a61567182821f37a178a.webm?t=1712662018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/8b070a742560a61567182821f37a178a.mp4?t=1712662018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 特点: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用链条摆动和推动，为发电机提供能量以完成关卡。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>全新的平台游戏运动机制！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>挑战自我，击败40个独特关卡！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以最短时间内完成关卡，解锁新的区域。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>回放并分享你的最佳表现。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在排行榜上竞争。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>安静地玩或疯狂地快速完成整个区域！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/6f8e00c69598f2657f5232add31eb17f.poster.avif?t=1712662018\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/6f8e00c69598f2657f5232add31eb17f.webm?t=1712662018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286720/extras/6f8e00c69598f2657f5232add31eb17f.mp4?t=1712662018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
